Class PreprocessDatasetFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.HistoricalFile
      • model.PreprocessDatasetFile

  • public class PreprocessDatasetFile
extends HistoricalFile
    This class defines the model for pre-processing the information of an intermediate or pre-processed dataset file.
